data.description: Absolutely Beautiful Home! 4 BR 3.5 Bathrooms in Oxford Park, master with whirlpool, separate shower, Double vanities, walk-in closet, Kitchen with granite, breakfast bar, walk-in pantry, opens to breakfast nook and open great living room with stone fireplace. Beamed vaulted ceilings, extensive hardwood floors and designer window treatment. Bonus office room, huge game room or 5th BR. Great space, Great Neighborhood, located close to pool, park and clubhouse. Large Corner Lot! This property MAY qualify for Seller Financing (Vendee).
